        "cn": "大型院校毕业晚会，演出形式以管弦乐与综合文艺节目为主。",
        "en": "A large-scale university graduation gala featuring orchestral and mixed performance formats."
      },
      "challenge": {
        "cn": "Behringer X32 现场输入通道全部插满，对通道管理、增益结构、编组控制和现场应变能力要求较高。管弦乐扩声更注重声部层次、整体动态和自然听感。",
        "en": "Full X32 channel count demanded rigorous gain structure, grouping and scene management. Orchestral reinforcement required natural dynamics and sectional balance."
      },
